Base Rule : Keep battle under control as well as battlefield , KO mob individual . Prevent mob aggro on non-combat member <br>
<br>
How to : Combat occur only under tankers spot . Caster keep away from battlefield in need . Caster need backoff at once when spell done and not got aggro . <br>
<br>
Procedure : <br>
1 , Main Tank response for call attack as well as keep mob aggro through taunt . <br>
2, Non-Main Tank draw in battlefield after main tank own the mob , remember use assist before  begin attack . <br>
3, During combat , taunt in need as well for non-main tankers as well but only often . <br>
4, Tankers , try your best to make damage under your aggro control . <br>
5, Caster , while mob's HP hit 50% , show off and done the mob as you can . <br>
6, Healer , please don't forget keep your enc alive<br>
<br>
Tactics by class - <br>
Tank:<br>
1, Main Tank response for target select and call attack <br>
2, Main Tank , taunt before attack to keep yourself at the top of the mob's hate list . This prevent enc got critical attack while mez broken accidently . <br>
3, Every combat begin by main tank in need , main tank able to call attack only while begin damaged by mob . <br>
4, Tanks surround the mob after got main tank's call attack . This prevent mob run like sissy to enlarge battlefield .<br>
5, Hot key amust , main tank : call attack , non-main tank : assist <br>
<br>
Debuffer and Enc :<br>
1, Keep close to tank's battlefield but keep in mind don't block tankers' sight <br>
2, ooc amust after debuff and mez , etc done <br>
<br>
Healer :<br>
1, Keep away from battlefield <br>
2, Main rule for healer : keep your Enc alive . Hot key for target enc help keep checking your enc <br>
3, assist main tank to check current battle status , but remember /assist off <br>
4, tank healing tactics : keep your target in range , idle 3 seconds after heal done . When you not got aggro , flee battlefield . If you got aggro after heal , be strong to stay and flee when tanks taunt off the mob .<br>
<br>
Casters :<br>
1, Keep away from battklefield<br>
2, You MUST NOT attack before tanks<br>
3, assist main tank to check current battle status , but remember /assist off <br>
4, Every DD only while target's HP hit 50%<br>
5, Nuke tactics : keep yoursel in battlefield , idle 3 seconds after you shot . When you not got aggro , flee battlefield . If you got aggro after shot , be your very strong to stay and flee when tanks taunt off the mob .<br>
